<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span> صحيح - <span class="c2">((صحيح أبي داود)</span>) <span class="c2">(٢٠٦١)</span> , <span class="c2">((الصحيحة)</span>) <span class="c2">(٢٢٠)</span>: ق.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>